{
  "stem": "9665.6",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "He arrived.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "And we got an-- offices in the [NON-ENGLISH] in The Hague.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "And I went to Czechoslovakia.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "And my friend, Barend Boers-- and I like to mention that-- started.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "He was a [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH] state for a waste merchant.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "He started doing compensation reciprocity transaction with Czechoslovakia and all other countries.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "And his first reciprocity was that he said, I will not do a deal-- because waste was very much in demand in those countries-- if there is not at least 5% or 10% in it for stockings.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "The stocking manufacturers in Czechoslovakia were not destroyed.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 62,
      "text": "There was a factory called [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 63,
      "text": "It was still intact.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 64,
      "text": "And I went to Prague, and we had to make these reciprocity or compensation transaction, which were very, very difficult, because there were 10 lines from Czechoslovakia.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 65,
      "text": "There were 8 lines from Holland.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 66,
      "text": "We had to balance it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 67,
      "text": "And it was up and down every two weeks to Prague.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 68,
      "text": "I can't say that I didn't enjoy this.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 69,
      "text": "The trip itself-- flying-- was never my scene.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 70,
      "text": "But Prague-- you know, this excitement suited me very, very well.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 71,
      "text": "And I can't-- oh, suited me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 72,
      "text": "I was excited, and I was young.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 73,
      "text": "And I-- these deals were very interesting.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 74,
      "text": "And it got to the stage-- and I must say, I must give it to my friend, Barend Boers, because I'm going to show that to his wife-- the late Barend Boers, to his wife-- that he was a fantastic friend for me.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 75,
      "text": "He was so good, and I'm still missing him.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 76,
      "text": "I was with him on the boat to Jamaica.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 77,
      "text": "I was with him in the plane to New York.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 78,
      "text": "I was with him together in Canada.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 79,
      "text": "And I was with him together in Dubocourt, Harwich, wherever we were stationed in England.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
